These are notes for the family of [Charles Curtis Brett]({{< relref
"charles-curtis-brett.pdc" >}}) and Ann Pilbean.

See [Charles Curtis Brett's wikitree
entry](https://www.wikitree.com/wiki/Brett-986).  This says that he married
Ann "Pilbin" on 12 June 1823.  The Dictionary of National Biography has this
as "Pilbean", and Ann's birth year as 1808/9 - see page on [John Brett
(painter)]({{< relref "john-brett-1831.pdc" >}}).

